    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO TOWER INC.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Inc.</strong> is not just a company—it's a <i>nightmare wrapped in corporate formality</i>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve signed up for what looked like a harmless job interview, but the higher you climb, the more you realize:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This company only hires survivors.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission: <strong>collect the quotes</strong>, escape using the elevator,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and pray your friends make it out alive…  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or sacrifice them before the tower claims you all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/0ce69adf43cd2f24ab4c848edd4b233f.poster.avif?t=1767544558\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/0ce69adf43cd2f24ab4c848edd4b233f.webm?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/0ce69adf43cd2f24ab4c848edd4b233f.mp4?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌑 FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floors of Horror</strong> – Each level hides <i>monsters, traps, and secrets</i> that shift with every run. Step wrong, and the building swallows you whole.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elevator Escape</strong> – Gather enough quotes and race back to safety. Will you wait for your team… or press the button and seal their fate?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo or Multiplayer</strong> – Survive the tower <u>alone</u> or with friends. Cooperation is powerful, but betrayal might be necessary.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Corporate Secrets</strong> – Items and environment objects can be <i>moved, manipulated, and exploited</i> in creative ways. The tower is alive—learn how to use it before it uses you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Employee’s Fate</strong> – Succeed and earn a shot at that <i>full-time contract</i>. Fail… and HR has a special place for you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/36218e1d078e1f6bf0f453ceb5fa5655.poster.avif?t=1767544558\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/36218e1d078e1f6bf0f453ceb5fa5655.webm?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/36218e1d078e1f6bf0f453ceb5fa5655.mp4?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 GAMEPLAY STYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Step into a world where every floor is <strong>unpredictable</strong>.</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Inc.</strong> combines tense exploration, high-stakes teamwork, and dark corporate humor,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >all under the constant looming threat of sacrifice, sabotage, and survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/144447cc2123a0e3abb2bb2dd60786b1.poster.avif?t=1767544558\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/144447cc2123a0e3abb2bb2dd60786b1.webm?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261310/extras/144447cc2123a0e3abb2bb2dd60786b1.mp4?t=1767544558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️ DANGERS AHEAD</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deadly <strong>traps</strong> hidden in plain sight.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creatures</strong> lurking behind doors and shadowed halls.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The constant ticking of <strong>time</strong>—take too long, and the building claims you.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Decisions that could <i>save the team</i>… or <u>end them instantly</u>.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📜 THE JOB OFFER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to climb the tower?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you balance <strong>greed</strong>, <strong>fear</strong>, and <strong>teamwork</strong> long enough to leave with your prize?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or will you be another <i>forgotten intern</i> in Tower Inc.’s endless halls?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The contract is waiting.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sign at your own risk.</strong></p>",
